overview: WWE Worlds Collide is a two-day professional wrestling show and WWE Network event featuring their 205 Live, NXT, and NXT UK brands. This event features the 15-man Worlds Collide tournament, with the wrestlers being equally divided amongst the NXT, NXT UK, and 205 Live rosters. Winner of said tournament receives an NXT Championship Title Match of their choosing.
title: WWE Worlds Collide
